<br>
The balance comes from the fact that we have no defense. With the increased damage that mobs are able to do now, and the static state of pet hps we have even less defense. A pet is about 8secs worth of a head start for running to the zone against PoP mobs. No runes, root, heals, instant succor, snares, slows, FD ect...allows us to wield offense like we do. It is about time and damn it we have earned it. I have heard melee complaining about the new mage water pet in regards to it assing mobs hehe.<br>
